Over 130 Community Leaders and Members Endorse Josh Schoemann For County Executive

Over 130 community leaders and members have endorsed our campaign. A county executive is accountable to the people. Period. As your county executive, I will engage the voters frequently. The county must ensure its budget priorities are yours so that the government lives within your means.
